metadata.title: Harbor seals skeletal and tissue samples

creators.name: University of Alaska Fairbanks (UAF), University of Alaska Museum

metadata.description:
Twelve communities in western Alaska will participate in collecting skeletal material (primarily skulls) and ultrafrozen tissues sample to be archived in the Alaska Frozen Tissue Collection.

An NPMR project
